2️⃣ GoLang Repository Job
Configuration
Job Type: Freestyle Project
Source Code Management: Git → GoLang repo
Build Steps:
Install dependencies (go mod tidy)
Run Unit Tests (go test ./... -v -coverprofile=coverage.out)
Static Analysis (golangci-lint run)
Reports & Artifacts
Code coverage report stored in Jenkins
Build logs archived as artifacts
📸 Screenshots
Job Configuration Screen → [Insert Image 3]
Test Output / Coverage Report → [Insert Image 4]
3️⃣ Java Repository Job
Configuration
Job Type: Freestyle Project
Source Code Management: Git → Java repo
Build Steps:
Maven Build (mvn clean install)
Unit Testing (mvn test)
Code Coverage (mvn jacoco:report)
Dependency / Vulnerability Scan (mvn dependency-check:check)
Reports & Artifacts
Test and coverage reports stored in Jenkins
Build artifacts archived locally or remotely
