Job Configuration Screen → [Insert Image 5]
Maven Build & Test Output → [Insert Image 6]
📦 Artifacts & Reports Management
Store CI reports and build artifacts in Jenkins workspace
Optionally, configure remote storage (NFS, S3, or shared server)
Access artifacts through Jenkins “Build Artifacts” section
🔔 Notifications

Configure failure notifications using:

Slack: Alerts in dedicated channel
Email: Jenkins SMTP configuration
Telegram: Webhook notifications (optional)
Notification Scenarios
Event	Notification Type
Build Fail	Slack + Email + Telegram
Build Pass	Optional Success Notification
