🔗 CI Job Flow Diagram
Python Job → GoLang Job → Java Job
          ↓
      Slack / Email / Telegram Notifications

Jobs are independent Freestyle Jobs but can be chained if required.

✅ Best Practices Implemented
Separate Freestyle Jobs per repository
CI Checks include Unit Tests, Linting, Security & Coverage
Artifacts stored and accessible via Jenkins
Failures trigger real-time notifications
Reports provide visibility into CI health
📌 Conclusion

This project demonstrates:

CI automation using Jenkins Freestyle Jobs
Multi-language repository integration (Python, GoLang, Java)
Artifact & report management
Advanced CI checks for quality assurance
Notification system for failure alerts
